  <AlienRace.ThingDef_AlienRace ParentName="BasePawn">
    <defName>Forge_Forgeling_Race</defName>
    <label>forgeling</label>
    <description>Long ago, a tribe of industrial zealots dabbled in an experimental technology that fused man and machine, giving rise to the Forgelings. A blend of steel and flesh, Forgelings consume chemfuel and wood to fuel a burning furnace within their chests. Pummeling metals into shape with their hammer-like fists, heating it with their burning forges, Forgelings make for excellent smiths.</description>
